{
  "stem": "322.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The following dawn-- you know, we arrived the, the 21st-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 19th, 20th-- on the 21st at dawn is when I saw a group of women and children crying and, and, and, and shouting for help.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I spotted a neighbor of ours, the Neuman family-- just her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is the way we called her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I looked, and I, I spotted my mother, too, and then my two sisters-- a 20-year-old and a 15-year-old.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then I found out what happened, of course, after I went home, that my mother assisted a neighbor of ours, a friend of ours, as a matter of fact, Irving Schwartz-- Irving's sister.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Niederman was her name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of the little girls was named after my, my grandmother, my mother's mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she-- my mother treasured that baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she assisted her in, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother was selected for the gas chamber as a result of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, my sister, my older sister was so close that she was not about to abandon my mother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So she, she was first selected for slave labor, and my 15-year-old sister also was selected for slave labor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But then she leaped across to be with her mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my kid sister followed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then when that was noticed by the selecting officer, shoved them back into the other line for slave labor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Another few minutes, my sister once again leaped across.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my kid sister followed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the following day at dawn, I saw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's why I saw them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this is why I-- see, you cannot survive without thought.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So what I did is I blinked it out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was out.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
